    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel so guilty. everytime my daughter comes over to help me with the groceries or the laundry, i can see how tired she is. she's always rushing off to something important. i feel like i'm just stealing her time and her energy. i don't want to be the reason they're always stressed out.",
